Sentencas: In the present study, correlation between solid oxide fuel cell anode microstructure and electrochemical performance during redox cycles was investigated.
Titulo: Quantitative analysis of solid oxide fuel cell anode microstructure change during redox cycles

Sentencas: Electrolyte-support cell with nickel/yttria stabilized zirconia composite anode was prepared and tested under discharge process with redox cycles.
Titulo: Quantitative analysis of solid oxide fuel cell anode microstructure change during redox cycles

Sentencas: Redox treatment was basically conducted every 20 h during discharge process.
Titulo: Quantitative analysis of solid oxide fuel cell anode microstructure change during redox cycles

Sentencas: Polarization resistance decreased just after redox treatment and increased during discharge process.
Titulo: Quantitative analysis of solid oxide fuel cell anode microstructure change during redox cycles

Sentencas: Enhancement of cell performance after every redox cycles and faster degradation in the following discharge process were observed.
Titulo: Quantitative analysis of solid oxide fuel cell anode microstructure change during redox cycles

Sentencas: Polarization resistance gradually increased as redox cycles were repeated.
Titulo: Quantitative analysis of solid oxide fuel cell anode microstructure change during redox cycles

Sentencas: Focused ion beam-scanning electron microscopy (FIB-SEM) observation was conducted for reconstructing the three dimensional microstructures of the tested samples.
Titulo: Quantitative analysis of solid oxide fuel cell anode microstructure change during redox cycles

Sentencas: From the three dimensional microstructure reconstruction, it is found that the shape of nickel particle got thinner and complicated after redox cycles.
Titulo: Quantitative analysis of solid oxide fuel cell anode microstructure change during redox cycles

Sentencas: Triple phase boundary (TPB) length increased after redox treatment and decreased after discharge process.
Titulo: Quantitative analysis of solid oxide fuel cell anode microstructure change during redox cycles

Sentencas: This TPB change was highly associated with Ni connectivity and Ni specific surface area.
Titulo: Quantitative analysis of solid oxide fuel cell anode microstructure change during redox cycles

Sentencas: These microstructure changes are consistent with the change of cell performance enhancement after redox treatment and degradation after discharge process.
Titulo: Quantitative analysis of solid oxide fuel cell anode microstructure change during redox cycles

Sentencas: However, TPB length density kept on increasing as redox cycles are repeated, which is inconsistent with the gradual degradation of anode performance.
Titulo: Quantitative analysis of solid oxide fuel cell anode microstructure change during redox cycles
